'''Ama Ata Aidoo''', ''née'' '''Christina Ama Aidoo''' (wavutse ku ya 23 Werurwe 1942) ni umwanditsi wo muri Gana, umusizi, umwanditsi w'amakinamico n'umunyeshuri.  Yari Minisitiri w’uburezi uyobowe na Jerry Rawlings administration . Mu 2000, yashinze Fondasiyo ya Mbaasem yo guteza imbere no gushyigikira umurimo w’abanditsi b’abagore [[Afurika|b’abanyafurika]].  

== Ubuzima bwo hambere ==
Aidoo yavutse ku ya 23 Werurwe 1942 i Saltpond mu mu gace ko hagati muri [[Gana]], Amakuru amwe arimo Megan Behrent, kaminuza ya Brown, na [[Afurika]] Ninde wavuze ko yavutse ku ya 31 Werurwe 1940.  

Yakuriye mu rugo rw'umwami wa Fante, umukobwa wa Nana Yaw Fama, umutware wa Abeadzi Kyiakor, na Maame Abasema. <ref>[https://www.taylorfrancis.com/books/e/9780203058558/chapters/10.4324/9780203058558-4 "AMA ATA AIDOO (1942-)"], ''Postcolonial African Writers'', Routledge, 1998.</ref> Yakuze mugihe cy' [[ubwongereza]] bushya bwa neocolonialism bwaberaga mu gihugu cye. Sekuru yiciwe na neocolonialiste, ibyo bikaba byaratumye se yibanda ku kamaro ko kwigisha abana n'imiryango yo mu mudugudu n'amateka yabayeho. Ibi byatumye afungura ishuri rya mbere mu mudugudu wabo maze bituma Aidoo yiga mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Wesley Girls aho yahisemo bwa mbere ko ashaka kuba umwanditsi. 

== Uburezi ==
Aidoo yize amashuri yisumbuye ya Wesley Girls i Cape Coast,  kuva 1961 kugeza 1964. Amashuri yisumbuye, yiyandikishije muri kaminuza ya Gana, muri Legon aho yakuye impamyabumenyi ya Bachelor of Arts mu Cyongereza ndetse yandika n'ikinamico ye ya mbere yise ''“Dilemma of Ghost”'', mu 1964. <ref>[http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/10410/Ama-Ata-Aidoo "Ama Ata Aidoo"], ''Encyclopædia Britannica''.</ref> Ikinamico yasohowe na Longman umwaka wakurikiyeho, bituma Aidoo aba umukinnyi wa mbere  w’amakinamico wo muri [[Afurika]]. <ref>Naana Banyiwa Horne, "Aidoo, Ama Ata", ''Who's Who in Contemporary Women's Writing'', 2001, Routledge.</ref>

== Filime ==
Niwe filime ya documentaire ya 2014, ''Ubuhanzi bwa Ama Ata Aidoo'', yakozwe na Yaba Badoe . <ref name="AAAA">[http://amaatafilm.com/ "The Art of Ama Ata Aidoo - a film by Yaba Badoe"], official website.</ref> <ref>Beti Ellerson, [http://africanwomenincinema.blogspot.co.uk/2013/12/yaba-badoe-talks-about-documentary-film.html "Yaba Badoe talks about the documentary film project 'The Art of Ama Ata Aidoo'"], African Women in Cinema, December 2013.</ref> <ref>Shakira Chambas and Sionne Neely, [http://www.awdf.org/the-art-of-ama-ata-aidoo-documentary-film-launch/ "The Art of AMA ATA AIDOO: Documentary Film Launch"], African Women’s Development Fund, 26 September 2014.</ref>

== Inyandiko ==
Ikinamico ya Aidoo irimo ''The Dilemma of Ghost'', yakorewe i Legon mu 1964 (yatangajwe bwa mbere 1965) na Pittsburgh mu 1988, na ''Anowa'', yasohowe mu 1971 ikorerwa i Londres mu 1991. 
